source: A cache rebuild may be required before changes take effect.
AddToAny is available on the "Manage display" pages of enabled entities, e.g. Structure > Content types > Article > Manage display.
Disabling may affect analytics and limit some functionality.
Perform administration tasks for the AddToAny module.
Provide share buttons for sharing the content.
Share buttons by AddToAny, including the AddToAny universal sharing button, Facebook, Twitter, Google+, Pinterest, and over 100 more on the AddToAny platform.
URL of the button image. Example: http://example.com/share.png

You can add HTML code to display customized standalone service buttons next to each universal share button. For example:
<a class="a2a_button_facebook"></a>
<a class="a2a_button_twitter"></a>
<a class="a2a_button_pinterest"></a>
You can add special CSS code for AddToAny. See AddToAny documentation.
You can add special JavaScript code for AddToAny. See AddToAny documentation.
